This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language understanding and text summarization. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses a data-driven approach and deep neural networks for summarization. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as summarization is a common task in this field. Finally, it could also be classified under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks for summarization.
